    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I created <a href="https://github.com/mrmans0n/site-mobilizer">this very little tiny project in Sinatra</a> for being able to obscure the usage of the <a href="https://www.readability.com/developers/api/parser">Readability&rsquo;s Parser API</a> token, as suggested in their documentation.</p>

<p>So, if you had any intention to use this, well&hellip; the little work you had to do is already taken care of.</p>
